# D{{N}} — Authorization / Visibility Matrix

**Audience:** Engineer + Compliance / Security (least-privilege conversations).
**When to look at this:** When designing role grants, reviewing audit logs, or answering "who can see X?". Required reading before any RBAC migration.
**Prose gap closed:** Glossary defines roles in isolation; canvases describe domain roles per BC; this diagram shows the **role × {{COLUMN_KIND}} permission grid** in one frame.

