## Who can read or write each {{COLUMN_KIND}}

### Reading order: matrix first, graph second

The **table below is canonical** (every role × every {{COLUMN_KIND}}). The
**companion flowchart** highlights only `RW` cells — the high-privilege
grants that warrant the strongest review.

|  | {{#COLUMNS}}**{{name}}** \| {{/COLUMNS}}
|---|{{#COLUMNS}}---|{{/COLUMNS}}
{{#ROLES}}
| **{{name}}**<br/><sub>{{scope_note}}</sub> | {{#permissions}}{{level}} \| {{/permissions}}
{{/ROLES}}

**Cell legend:** `R` = read · `W` = write · `RW` = read+write · `—` = no access

```mermaid
