## Legend

| Symbol | Meaning |
|--------|---------|
| Yellow node | Role (named principal) |
| Blue node | {{COLUMN_KIND}} scope (aggregate or BC) |
| `==>` edge | High-privilege `RW` grant |
| `R` cell | Role can read this scope |
| `W` cell | Role can write but not read back |
| `RW` cell | Role can read and write |
| `—` cell | No access — least-privilege default |

